OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, then clear spells
OL,7,Fovernight, with occasionally heavy
OL,8,Fshowers. Touch of frost possible in
OL,9,Fsheltered spots, but northwesterly
OL,10,Fwinds starting to freshen towards end
OL,11,Fof night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAnother rather cold day with
OL,14,Fa mix of sunny spells and showers, the
OL,15,Fshowers heavy at times. Winds turning
OL,16,Fnortherly and becoming strong at times
OL,17,Fin coastal parts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
