OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells Friday with showers and
OL,7,Fnortherly winds easing. Mainly dry
OL,8,FSaturday with spells of sunshine and
OL,9,Flight winds. Dry start Sunday but
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain edging eats in
OL,11,Fafternoon.
